<paragraph id="99EF01C63F11AED946E4B32EA2193263" pageId="0" pageNumber="21">Type protologue.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="77B753C96D452B69E98484354A3A4268" pageId="0" pageNumber="21">
T. Nari Khorsum, 
<emphasis id="8E4C84CB24B33F076421939A84F5058E" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="21">H. v. Schlagintweit</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="6937DC7D73A5166BE662410F829F06FC" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="21">Type</emphasis>
: [China] Tibet, Gnari (Nari) Khorsum, alt. 5000 m, 5-15 Sep 1855, 
<emphasis id="5AFA1E1BE1A293E6EAF04A60E5A54117" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="21">Schlagintweit 7116</emphasis>
